## ðŸŽ¨ UI State Management

### Loading States
```typescript
// Global loading state
setLoading: (loading) => set({ isLoading: loading }),

// Usage in components
const { isLoading, setLoading } = useAppStore();

const handleAsyncOperation = async () => {
  setLoading(true);
  try {
    await someAsyncOperation();
  } finally {
    setLoading(false);
  }
};
```

### Theme Management
```typescript
